cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper deals with image representation and retrieval, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of deep CNN features also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques for text-based image retrieval, which could relate to the computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
